"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## About\\n\\nFor the Admins of Mundo Lingo community on telegram. Here we coordinate administration, share ideas and feedback. Be attentive to new instructions given by the Assembly Leads.\\n\\nNot already in **Online Assembly?** You should first join [Mundo Lingo Collaborators](https://mirror.xyz/0xe2A039aB83dB1ea76842FEc23611806d50C4B4Ae/onyNgQAi-2VKGNTDGYK9vf20AK-k7i-3qot58G4Qo54) and then apply to be an **Admin** here: \\n\\n[https://form.typeform.com/to/Rg2Snz](https://form.typeform.com/to/Rg2Snz)\\n\\n### Groups AKA “Rooms”\\n\\nThere are currently 17 Rooms, each represents a different country. Members converse in the target language. Access to these chat rooms is given via the [Mundo Lingo Lobby](https://t.me/mundolingo_lobby).\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/bnYVVuhsPhQPo3SkiZmKz.png?height=911&width=1419)\\n\\n## Apply to be an Admin\\n\\nWoohoo! We’d love to hear from you. Please apply via [Mundo Lingo Collaborators](https://mirror.xyz/0xe2A039aB83dB1ea76842FEc23611806d50C4B4Ae/onyNgQAi-2VKGNTDGYK9vf20AK-k7i-3qot58G4Qo54)\\n\\n## Admin Responsibilities\\n\\n### Moderate the group\\n\\nGroup rules are pinned to the top of every Room. We use the same criteria in all our online forums to delete, remove and ban **\\\\[Link Needed\\\\]**\\n\\n### Detect and remove spam\\n\\nIt’s not required to read every message. Skim through quickly and look for suspicious content. Encourage members to alert and tag admins when there’s spam.\\n\\n### Foster conversation\\n\\nIn the beginning small groups risk being too quiet. Here’s some tips to foster conversation:\\n\\n* Welcoming new people to the Room\\n* Ask them to introduce themselves\\n* Inserting new topics, memes, questions\\n* Post Regular Activities (see below)\\n\\n## Activities\\n\\nThere are 4 available weekly **Activities**. Find volunteers (other members) for each and delegate them the responsibility to post the Activity images each week and to repost it from time to time to make sure new members can join.\\n\\n### Diary day Sunday\\n\\nShare Selfies, foodie pics, quarantine experiences, city life. Tell us what you’ve been up to this week! Funny stories, life hacks, scary moments, anything.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/zCx05ReIGD3jxGwEYv-xE.png?height=241&width=845)\\n\\n### Meme Monday\\n\\nShare with us your sharpest, smartest and even most borderline controversial memes you can muster. Let the meme wars begin!\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/9npAQQ20WhY1a-n7uR1CG.png?height=241&width=845)\\n\\n### Video Tuesday\\n\\nUse the telescope function within telegram to send videos into the group. Drop us an intro, something interesting, if you’re singing or playing a song. Anything goes. It’s also another way to practise speaking!\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/-mWrHK2p90fi1GazfWBSi.png?height=241&width=845)\\n\\n### Audio Fridays\\n\\nSend voice notes to practice your speaking skills. Tell us about your day, your favourite animals, your best memories or just how you’re feeling.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/2cE4PuhV4-giGe-gMWhlJ.png?height=241&width=845)\\n\\n### Live Rooms\\n\\nLive Rooms allow participants to talk in real-time with voice and optional video. Hosting a regular live room increases member participation and reduces shyness… and it’s kinda fun. [Here’s how](https://telegram.org/blog/group-video-calls?ln=r).\\n\\n### Save Time\\n\\nSchedule **Activity** posts in advance. Hold down the ‘Send’ button and select ‘Schedule Message’. Full [instructions here](https://telegram.org/blog/scheduled-reminders-themes).\\n\\n### Translate\\n\\nCommunications and instructions in the Online Assembly are given in English. Translate any official announcements into your Room’s language.\\n\\n## Answering FAQs\\n\\n* \\\\*\\\\*How to find group?\\n  \\\\*\\\\*Send users to the Mundo Lingo Lobby. There they’ll find a list of the chat rooms.\\n* \\\\*\\\\*How to join the Live Room?\\n  \\\\*\\\\*Anyone can start a the Live Room at any time but ask around in the group first to build consensus on a time. Here’s [how to open the feature](https://telegram.org/blog/group-video-calls?ln=r).\\n* \\\\*\\\\*How to use the Telescope feature for Video Tuesday?\\n  \\\\*\\\\*To send a video message, tap the mic icon to switch to camera mode. Tap and hold the camera icon and record a video message. When you’re done, just release the recording button to dispatch your message. [More info here…](https://telegram.org/blog/video-messages-and-telescope)\",\"timestamp\":1637832565,\"title\":\"The Online Assembly\"},\"digest\":\"97rB8pfQ0RmtWsT4tVos-N5Pao6mwHeMHHVgfruciT8\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xe2A039aB83dB1ea76842FEc23611806d50C4B4Ae\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"F8zG1zTeZMDpV2_EIlWrsKpmnGDh3SxjOF71ivpgrJg\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"cTaiHvTF70f6CzGg3oqJ4Z5azdotT-0kGnHltBTC7IE\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"98LhLDFUCd0K5DUYg0uiRYZpkFGNNBRaMjz46A2EtVf5irPlu-eCAUI-epymt-Yc1GKQUE9sPBIUaOaCYXG8Jg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x9ffe03abbb74481883195e9c49f74ad3362bbcc9be4787bc7d86b31ee0a27a51494508e5274ca44c64dfc0a67507f0b6354439a75b1d7c337ff95a9f16a6c4c11b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"F8zG1zTeZMDpV2_EIlWrsKpmnGDh3SxjOF71ivpgrJg\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"cTaiHvTF70f6CzGg3oqJ4Z5azdotT-0kGnHltBTC7IE\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"YHiCb5_XaYGdpbRypQWQkl09ptcQ-gQ4z3xVB_ChbDc\"}"